songs.title: Mad At You

Ooh, ooh-ooh
Ooh, ooh-ooh
Ooh, ooh-ooh
Ooh, ooh-ooh
Ooh, ooh-ooh
Ooh, ooh-ooh

I'm takin' chances with this 22

Fuck you think?
Walkin' out the bank with blue face hundreds, yeah, yeah, yeah

Trynna finesse me, is you forreal? (Is you for real?)

All my niggas drill, what's the deal? (What's the deal?)
